  "title": "Adapted Origins - An Origins Addon",
  "description": "Adds several community-made Origins that I have revised and rebalanced. Requires Origins.",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/origination-fabric\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/r8KbnyM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"396\" /></strong></span></a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>This mod is packaged and intended to be used with the <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/origination-fabric\">Origination Modpack</a>.&nbsp;Go check it out!</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Requires <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/origins\">Origins </a>and <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pehkui\">Pehkui</a>.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">Adds several reimagined and revised Origins as an addition to the Origins mod:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">Giant [<a href=\"https://origination.gitbook.io/origination-1.19.2/origins-information/list-of-playable-origins/giant\">Wiki</a>]</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">A towering Origin that has greater strength and the ability to carry and throw entities, but has a drawback in size and speed.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">Dullahan&nbsp;[<a href=\"https://origination.gitbook.io/origination-1.19.2/origins-information/list-of-playable-origins/dullahan\">Wiki</a>]</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">A ghostly rider that can summon a nightmare steed to ride and is empowered to hunt for souls at night.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">Fairy&nbsp;[<a href=\"https://origination.gitbook.io/origination-1.19.2/origins-information/list-of-playable-origins/fairy\">Wiki</a>]</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">A small protector, with a set of wings and the ability to heal and guide their allies.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">Copper Golem&nbsp;[<a href=\"https://origination.gitbook.io/origination-1.19.2/origins-information/list-of-playable-origins/copper-golem\">Wiki</a>]</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">A curious automaton, equipped with sensors to find rare materials as well as skills to help create redstone contraptions.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">Forestborn&nbsp;[<a href=\"https://origination.gitbook.io/origination-1.19.2/origins-information/list-of-playable-origins/forestborn\">Wiki</a>]</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">A being of the wilds, capable of phasing through trees and becoming empowered when surrounded by nature.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">Phoenix [<a href=\"https://origination.gitbook.io/origination-1.19.2/origins-information/list-of-playable-origins/phoenix\">Wiki</a>]</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 14px;\">A noble firebird, who can become reborn after dying and fly with their wings.</span></li>\n</ul>",
